lines.text: Oh, you can have your squirrel and possum and bear/But give me that little feller walkin' back thar!

[to audience]
This bellhop's a square for fair!
Florida, the alligator state. Here, deep in the heart of the Everglades, lives the hungry alligator, ever on the search for any morsel of food.
Where'd my pie go? What happened to my pie?
I want to settle my bill, buster.
